data.description: SPECTACULAR VIEW OVERLOOKING park & city!  Situated on TWO LOTS adjacent to Marquam Nature Park and BEAUTIFUL SW HILLS TRAILS. This diamond in the rough has AMAZING MAIN FLOOR LIVING with large rooms and plenty of light filled windows! Three bedrooms plus office. Downstairs could be separate living, short-term rental, or use as one large home.  OVERSIZED GARAGE has tons of storage.  Enjoy the EXPANSIVE DECKS while admiring nature!  Truly AMAZING LOCATION with deer walking by on a regular basis.  Contact your agent for additional details regarding this sale.  Best deal in neighborhood!!! [Home Energy Score = 2. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10047915]
